# Landing bootstrap seeds default published content when DB is empty.
# See CMS-RUNBOOK.md for Astro STRAPI_URL / token variables (configured in the frontend repo).

# Strapi admin “Open preview” (https://docs.strapi.io/cms/features/preview)
# CLIENT_URL = public Astro site origin, no trailing slash, e.g. https://mantis-public-2025-deployment.vercel.app
# PREVIEW_SECRET = long random string; same value must be set as PREVIEW_SECRET on Vercel for the Astro app.
#CLIENT_URL=
#PREVIEW_SECRET=
